{"tid":1006244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾球員賤種朗 真正實力數據update 20190203","createTime":"2019-02-02T21:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T07:16:03.000Z","uid":54373,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3fea95fc8a808402112738b7562ac54aaadc10","tid":1006244,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T21:28:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美斯又拯救球隊<br />\n賤種朗？</span><br />\n<br />\n本週<br />\n賤種朗 - 10射2入 (對升班馬失分)<br />\n美斯 - 8射2入 (1球12m)<br />\n<br />\n#數據post目的係唔想班賤朗迷再呃人<br />\n#上述數據由今季第1場比賽開始計算<br />\n#上述數據根據 who scored + 7m 賽後數據 每場累積而來<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 144射17入球 (5球靠12碼) (11.8%)<br />\n歐聯: 27射1入球 1紅牌 (3.7%)<br />\n意大利社區盾 6射1入 (16.6%)<br />\n意大利盃: n射0入<span style=\"color: red;\"> (0%入球率 已修業)</span><br />\n(190113vs 榜尾博洛尼亞, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n(190131vs 中游阿特蘭大, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n<strong><br />\n已射177球 得個19個入球 合共10.7%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 97射21入球 (2球靠12碼) (21.6%)<br />\n歐聯: 20射6入球 0紅牌 (30%)<br />\n西班牙盃: n射2入<br />\n(190118vs 中游利雲特入1, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n(190131vs 強隊西維爾入1, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>已117射入29球 合共24.78%</strong>"},{"pid":"e7f5befea6e4c6a2d0377ac4c291203b2862e03f","tid":1006244,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T21:28:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美斯拋離C朗 10球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"18527ad5ecabed2fd9fe547f4bc9f496f37a1675","tid":1006244,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T21:28:53.000Z","msg":"騎仔咁夜唔訓睇牙朗？"},{"pid":"094ff64d3b34a